{
  "video_id": "HR9956gDpUY",
  "title": "A plan to recycle the unrecyclable | Ashton Cofer",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12693.0,
      "end_time": 15116.0,
      "text": "It was just an ordinary Saturday."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15140.0,
      "end_time": 17356.0,
      "text": "My dad was outside mowing the lawn,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 17380.0,
      "end_time": 19636.0,
      "text": "my mom was upstairs folding laundry,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19660.0,
      "end_time": 21796.0,
      "text": "my sister was in her room doing homework"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 21820.0,
      "end_time": 24180.0,
      "text": "and I was in the basement playing video games."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24900.0,
      "end_time": 27235.0,
      "text": "And as I came upstairs to get something to drink,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 28476.0,
      "text": "I looked out the window"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28500.0,
      "end_time": 31796.0,
      "text": "and realized that there was something that I was supposed to be doing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 31820.0,
      "end_time": 33200.0,
      "text": "and this is what I saw."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35700.0,
      "end_time": 38796.0,
      "text": "No, this wasn&#39;t my family&#39;s dinner on fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 38820.0,
      "end_time": 41460.0,
      "text": "This was my science project."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42600.0,
      "end_time": 43516.0,
      "text": "Flames were pouring out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 43540.0,
      "end_time": 44756.0,
      "text": "smoke was in the air"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 44780.0,
      "end_time": 47996.0,
      "text": "and it looked like our wooden deck was about to catch fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 48200.0,
      "end_time": 49836.0,
      "text": "I immediately started yelling."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 49860.0,
      "end_time": 51356.0,
      "text": "My mom was freaking out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 51380.0,
      "end_time": 53476.0,
      "text": "my dad ran around to put out the fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 53500.0,
      "end_time": 57636.0,
      "text": "and of course my sister started recording a Snapchat video."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 57660.0,
      "end_time": 59556.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 59580.0,
      "end_time": 62780.0,
      "text": "This was just the beginning of my team&#39;s science project."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 63300.0,
      "end_time": 65956.0,
      "text": "My team is composed of me and three other students"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 65980.0,
      "end_time": 67660.0,
      "text": "who are here in the audience today."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 68100.0,
      "end_time": 70116.0,
      "text": "We competed in FIRST LEGO League"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 70140.0,
      "end_time": 73676.0,
      "text": "which is an international LEGO robotics competition for kids,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 73700.0,
      "end_time": 75556.0,
      "text": "and in addition to a robotics game,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 75580.0,
      "end_time": 77956.0,
      "text": "we also worked on a separate science project,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 77980.0,
      "end_time": 80676.0,
      "text": "and this was the project that we were working on."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 80700.0,
      "end_time": 82676.0,
      "text": "So the idea for this project all started"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 82700.0,
      "end_time": 83956.0,
      "text": "when a few months earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 83980.0,
      "end_time": 86796.0,
      "text": "a couple of my teammates took a trip to Central America"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 86820.0,
      "end_time": 89315.0,
      "text": "and saw beaches littered with Styrofoam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 89340.0,
      "end_time": 91300.0,
      "text": "or expanded polystyrene foam."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 91860.0,
      "end_time": 93996.0,
      "text": "And when they came back and told us about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94200.0,
      "end_time": 97716.0,
      "text": "we really started thinking about the ways in which we see Styrofoam every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 97740.0,
      "end_time": 99356.0,
      "text": "Get a new flat-screen TV?"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 99380.0,
      "end_time": 102339.0,
      "text": "You end up with a block of Styrofoam bigger than the TV itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 102900.0,
      "end_time": 104356.0,
      "text": "Drink a cup of coffee?"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 104380.0,
      "end_time": 107556.0,
      "text": "Well, those Styrofoam coffee cups are sure going to add up."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 107580.0,
      "end_time": 110956.0,
      "text": "And where do all these items go after their one-time use?"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 110980.0,
      "end_time": 114396.0,
      "text": "Since there aren&#39;t any good existing solutions for used Styrofoam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 114420.0,
      "end_time": 116956.0,
      "text": "almost all of them end up right in the landfill,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 116980.0,
      "end_time": 118316.0,
      "text": "or the oceans and beaches,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 118340.0,
      "end_time": 121360.0,
      "text": "taking over 500 years to degrade."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 121600.0,
      "end_time": 123276.0,
      "text": "And in fact, every year, the US alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 123300.0,
      "end_time": 125956.0,
      "text": "produces over two billion pounds of Styrofoam,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 125980.0,
      "end_time": 129156.0,
      "text": "filling up a staggering 25 percent of landfills."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 129180.0,
      "end_time": 132260.0,
      "text": "So why do we have these ghost accumulations of Styrofoam waste?"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 132860.0,
      "end_time": 135660.0,
      "text": "Why can&#39;t we just recycle them like many plastics?"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 136220.0,
      "end_time": 139636.0,
      "text": "Well, simply put, recycled polystyrene is too expensive"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 139660.0,
      "end_time": 141236.0,
      "text": "and potentially contaminated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 145476.0,
      "text": "so there is very little market demand for Styrofoam that has to be recycled."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 145500.0,
      "end_time": 149360.0,
      "text": "And as a result, Styrofoam is considered a nonrenewable material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 149600.0,
      "end_time": 152820.0,
      "text": "because it is neither feasible nor viable to recycle polystyrene."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 153420.0,
      "end_time": 155995.0,
      "text": "And in fact, many cities across the US"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 156200.0,
      "end_time": 157436.0,
      "text": "have even passed ordinances"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157460.0,
      "end_time": 161760.0,
      "text": "that simply ban the production of many products containing polystyrene,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 161100.0,
      "end_time": 163156.0,
      "text": "which includes disposable utensils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163180.0,
      "end_time": 165356.0,
      "text": "packing peanuts, takeout containers"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165380.0,
      "end_time": 167516.0,
      "text": "and even plastic beach toys,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 167540.0,
      "end_time": 170516.0,
      "text": "all products that are very useful in today&#39;s society."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 170540.0,
      "end_time": 172715.0,
      "text": "And now France has become the first country"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 172740.0,
      "end_time": 174996.0,
      "text": "to completely ban all plastic utensils,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 175200.0,
      "end_time": 176620.0,
      "text": "cups and plates."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 177100.0,
      "end_time": 179516.0,
      "text": "But what if we could keep using Styrofoam"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 179540.0,
      "end_time": 183275.0,
      "text": "and keep benefiting from its cheap, lightweight, insulating"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 183300.0,
      "end_time": 185360.0,
      "text": "and excellent packing ability,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 185600.0,
      "end_time": 187396.0,
      "text": "while not having to suffer from the repercussions"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 187420.0,
      "end_time": 188739.0,
      "text": "of having to dispose of it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 189140.0,
      "end_time": 192636.0,
      "text": "What if we could turn it into something else that&#39;s actually useful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 192660.0,
      "end_time": 195220.0,
      "text": "What if we could make the impossible possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 196220.0,
      "end_time": 200796.0,
      "text": "My team hypothesized that we could use the carbon that&#39;s already in Styrofoam"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 200820.0,
      "end_time": 202516.0,
      "text": "to create activated carbon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 202540.0,
      "end_time": 204900.0,
      "text": "which is used in almost every water filter today."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 205300.0,
      "end_time": 208916.0,
      "text": "And activated carbon works by using very small micropores"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 208940.0,
      "end_time": 211900.0,
      "text": "to filter out contaminants from water or even air."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 212660.0,
      "end_time": 215835.0,
      "text": "So we started out by doing a variety of heating tests,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 215860.0,
      "end_time": 218940.0,
      "text": "and unfortunately, we had many failures."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 219460.0,
      "end_time": 221996.0,
      "text": "Literally, nothing worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 222200.0,
      "end_time": 224276.0,
      "text": "Besides my dad&#39;s grill catching on fire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 224300.0,
      "end_time": 226956.0,
      "text": "most of our samples vaporized into nothing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 226980.0,
      "end_time": 229396.0,
      "text": "or exploded inside expensive furnaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 229420.0,
      "end_time": 231660.0,
      "text": "leaving a horribly sticky mess."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235859.0,
      "text": "In fact, we were so saddened by our failures that we almost gave up."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 237180.0,
      "end_time": 238516.0,
      "text": "So why did we keep trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 238540.0,
      "end_time": 240916.0,
      "text": "when all the adults said it was impossible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 240940.0,
      "end_time": 243859.0,
      "text": "Well, maybe it&#39;s because we&#39;re kids. We don&#39;t know any better."
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 244599.0,
      "end_time": 248760.0,
      "text": "But the truth is, we kept trying because we thought it was still possible."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 248100.0,
      "end_time": 249796.0,
      "text": "We knew that if we were successful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 249820.0,
      "end_time": 253236.0,
      "text": "we would be helping the environment and making the world a better place."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 254916.0,
      "text": "So we kept trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 254940.0,
      "end_time": 256676.0,
      "text": "and failing"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 256700.0,
      "end_time": 258356.0,
      "text": "and trying"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 258380.0,
      "end_time": 259956.0,
      "text": "and failing."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 259980.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261620.00000000003,
      "text": "We were so ready to give up."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 262460.0,
      "end_time": 264360.0,
      "text": "But then it happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 264600.0,
      "end_time": 266756.0,
      "text": "With the right temperatures, times and chemicals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 266780.0,
      "end_time": 269350.0,
      "text": "we finally got that successful test result"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 269600.0,
      "end_time": 272875.0,
      "text": "showing us that we had created activated carbon from Styrofoam waste."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 272899.0,
      "end_time": 275476.0,
      "text": "And at that moment, the thing that had been impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 275500.0,
      "end_time": 276740.0,
      "text": "all of a sudden wasn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 277300.0,
      "end_time": 280356.0,
      "text": "It showed us that although we had many failures at the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 280380.0,
      "end_time": 284760.0,
      "text": "we were able to persevere through them to get the test results that we wanted."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 284100.0,
      "end_time": 287360.0,
      "text": "And moreover, not only were we able to create activated carbon"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 287600.0,
      "end_time": 288316.0,
      "text": "for purifying water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 288340.0,
      "end_time": 290796.0,
      "text": "but we were also able to reduce Styrofoam waste,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 290820.0,
      "end_time": 293580.0,
      "text": "solving two global problems with just one solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 294140.0,
      "end_time": 297750.0,
      "text": "So from then on, we were inspired to take our project further,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 297100.0,
      "end_time": 299316.0,
      "text": "performing more tests to make it more effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 299340.0,
      "end_time": 301676.0,
      "text": "and testing it in real world situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 301700.0,
      "end_time": 303436.0,
      "text": "We then proceeded to receive funding"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 303460.0,
      "end_time": 306436.0,
      "text": "from the NSTA&#39;s eCYBERMISSION STEM-in-Action program"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 306460.0,
      "end_time": 308195.0,
      "text": "sponsored by the US Army,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 308220.0,
      "end_time": 310596.0,
      "text": "as well as FIRST Global Innovation Awards"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 310620.0,
      "end_time": 311900.0,
      "text": "sponsored by XPRIZE."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 312460.0,
      "end_time": 313715.0,
      "text": "And we were also honored"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 313740.0,
      "end_time": 316516.0,
      "text": "with the Scientific American Innovator Award"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 316540.0,
      "end_time": 317780.0,
      "text": "from Google Science Fair."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 318300.0,
      "end_time": 321756.0,
      "text": "And using these funds, we plan to file a full patent on our process"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 321780.0,
      "end_time": 323659.0,
      "text": "and to continue to work on our project."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 328436.0,
      "text": "So yes, although we started with catching my dad&#39;s grill on fire"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 328460.0,
      "end_time": 330955.0,
      "text": "and failing so many times that we almost quit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 330980.0,
      "end_time": 333516.0,
      "text": "it was well worth it when we look back at it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 333540.0,
      "end_time": 336356.0,
      "text": "We took a problem that many people said was impossible"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 336380.0,
      "end_time": 337876.0,
      "text": "and we made it possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 337900.0,
      "end_time": 341155.0,
      "text": "and we persevered when it looked like nothing that we did would work."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 341180.0,
      "end_time": 343276.0,
      "text": "We learned that you can&#39;t have success"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 343300.0,
      "end_time": 344796.0,
      "text": "without a little,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 344820.0,
      "end_time": 346580.0,
      "text": "or a lot, of failure."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 347260.0,
      "end_time": 350876.0,
      "text": "So in the future, don&#39;t be afraid if your grill goes up in flames,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 350900.0,
      "end_time": 354780.0,
      "text": "because you never know when your idea might just catch fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 355620.0,
      "end_time": 356836.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 356860.0,
      "end_time": 360340.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}